data.description: Nestled on nearly 5 acres of picturesque land, this charming country home has undergone recent renovations, making it a true gem in Nassau County's coveted A-rated school district. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, with over 1,500 sqft of living space, this residence offers a seamless open-concept design that exudes warmth and comfort. Enjoy tranquil sunsets on the front porch as deer graze in the yard. Inside, a wood-burning fireplace adds rustic charm to the living area. The spacious kitchen is a culinary dream. The owner's suite boasts two walk-in closets. Recent upgrades include luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout, fresh paint, a new roof (Dec '21), a water softener/filtration system (Jan '22), and a new well pump/tank (Feb '22). With approximately 4 acres of land cleared, you have space for outdoor pursuits, and the home offers seclusion just 30 minutes from Downtown Jacksonville and 20 minutes from Callahan.
